  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  BSA

          -  Receiving stable infusion of one high dose inotrope or two medium dose inotropes for a
             respective minimum time indicated.

          -  C.I.

          -  Elevated Filling Pressures, PCWP or PA

          -  Time to enrollment within 48 hours from weaning

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Renal dysfunction

          -  Hepatic dysfunction

          -  Right Ventricular failure defined.

          -  LV or RV Thrombus

          -  Other exclusions per protocol
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
